{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SettingsSchemaKeyRef\/getRange()"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"getRange","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib10VariantRefV","text":"VariantRef","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"!","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This function will return a [Variant](\/\/documentation\/glib\/variant that fully describes the range"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"of values that are valid for "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"key"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The type of [Variant](\/\/documentation\/glib\/variant returned is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"(sv)"},{"text":". The string describes","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the type of range restriction in effect. The type and meaning of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the value contained in the variant depends on the string.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the string is "},{"code":"'type'","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" then the variant contains an empty array."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"The element type of that empty array is the expected type of value"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"and all values of that type are valid.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the string is "},{"code":"'enum'","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" then the variant contains an array","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"enumerating the possible values. Each item in the array is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a possible valid value and no other values are valid."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If the string is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"'flags'"},{"text":" then the variant contains an array. Each","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"item in the array is a value that may appear zero or one times in an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"array to be used as the value for this key. For example, if the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"variant contained the array "},{"code":"['x', 'y']","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" then the valid values for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the key would be "},{"code":"[]","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"['x']"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"['y']"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"['x', 'y']"},{"text":" and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"['y', 'x']","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Finally, if the string is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"'range'"},{"type":"text","text":" then the variant contains a pair"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"of like-typed values – the minimum and maximum permissible values"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"for this key."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This information should not be used by normal programs.  It is"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"considered to be a hint for introspection purposes.  Normal programs","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"should already know what is permitted by their own schema.  The"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"format may change in any way in the future – but particularly, new"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"forms may be added to the possibilities described above."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You should free the returned value with "},{"code":"g_variant_unref()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" when it is","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"no longer needed."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/settingsschemakeyref\/getrange()"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"metadata":{"externalID":"s:3GIO25SettingsSchemaKeyProtocolPAAE8getRange4GLib10VariantRefVSgyF::SYNTHESIZED::s:3GIO20SettingsSchemaKeyRefV","title":"getRange()","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"getRange","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"() -> "},{"text":"VariantRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib10VariantRefV","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"!","kind":"text"}],"modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"symbolKind":"method","extendedModule":"GIO","roleHeading":"Instance Method","role":"symbol"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Queries the range of a key."}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SettingsSchemaKeyRef","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SettingsSchemaKeyRef\/SettingsSchemaKeyProtocol-Implementations"]]},"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/SettingsSchemaKey":{"abstract":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SettingsSchemaKey","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" is an opaque data structure and can only be accessed"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"using the following functions."}],"url":"\/documentation\/gio\/settingsschemakey","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"SettingsSchemaKey","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"SettingsSchemaKey"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"SettingsSchemaKey","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SettingsSchemaKey"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","title":"GIO","url":"\/documentation\/gio","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/SettingsSchemaKeyRef/getRange()":{"fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"getRange"},{"kind":"text","text":"() -> "},{"text":"VariantRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib10VariantRefV"},{"text":"!","kind":"text"}],"title":"getRange()","abstract":[{"text":"Queries the range of a key.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/settingsschemakeyref\/getrange()","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SettingsSchemaKeyRef\/getRange()","role":"symbol"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/SettingsSchemaKeyRef/SettingsSchemaKeyProtocol-Implementations":{"abstract":[],"title":"SettingsSchemaKeyProtocol Implementations","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SettingsSchemaKeyRef\/SettingsSchemaKeyProtocol-Implementations","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/settingsschemakeyref\/settingsschemakeyprotocol-implementations","kind":"article","type":"topic","role":"collectionGroup"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/SettingsSchemaKeyRef":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"SettingsSchemaKeyRef"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/settingsschemakeyref","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SettingsSchemaKeyRef","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"SettingsSchemaKeyRef"}],"abstract":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SettingsSchemaKey","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" is an opaque data structure and can only be accessed"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"using the following functions.","ty